data.description: Beautiful and well maintained two-story single family home in the heart of Raleigh. Located in Granite Ridge community, just minutes to downtown Raleigh, White Oak shopping, with quick and convenient access to 1-40, 440 Beltline. Water heater in 2019, Garage door openers in 2021, Gas fireplace, electric range. All appliances and TVs in home will convey.         Welcome Home!    * 2/1 UPDATE!  New Month, New Update! Seller is now offering $2000 credit at closing in lieu of carpet replacement! *
